      "span_text": "By co-expressing CAPTURE1.0 (FB-dCas9 and BirA) and a validated sgRNA targeting HBG1/2 promoters, we detected 740-fold on-target enrichment relative to the nearby non-targeted HBB promoter (Additional file 1: Figure S1b )."
